# 🛒 E-commerce Sales & Customer Analytics Project  
![SQL](https://img.shields.io/badge/SQL-Server-blue?logo=databricks&logoColor=white)  
![Power BI](https://img.shields.io/badge/PowerBI-Dashboard-yellow?logo=powerbi&logoColor=white)  
